     * Vietnamese

   These materials were developed as a general guide and are not intended
   as legal advice.

   The information in this brochure contains Washington State Law. DSHS
   Aging and Adult Services Administration convened the Task Force on the
   Patient Self-Determination Act to develop this brochure. The Task Force
   included advocates, lawyers, nursing home administrators, nursing home
   residents, and state employees.

   Medicaid for People Who Need Long Term Care

   This brochure is for people who need help paying for their long-term
   care.

